description: Distribution of Fisheries values in the NMC region layer/data shows the distribution of Fisheries landed  value in million USD per year.  Fisheries landed value data was derived from the study "Understanding and Valuing the Marine Ecosystem Services of the Northern Mozambique Channel " by Paulo A.L.D. Nunes and Andrea Ghermandi. This study aimed to understand and value the coastal and marine ecosystem services in the Northern Mozambique Channel region (NMC).
name: Distribution of Fisheries landed values in the NMC region
